<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Musée du Louvre</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8" name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #4583E5;
    }

    /* Remove the navbar's default margin-bottom and rounded borders */ 
    .navbar {
      margin-bottom: 0;
      border-radius: 0;
        padding-left: 0px;
    }
    .text_index{
        text-align: justify;
    }
    label {
      width: 50%;
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: block;
    }
    input, #champs_input, .champs_input, .champs_country{
      width: 50%;
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: block;
    }

    input[type="checkbox"]{
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-left: 0px;
      width: 13px;
    }
    .btn{
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      width: 100px;
    }
    .container_visitor, .container_ticket{
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    /* Set height of the grid so .sidenav can be 100% (adjust as needed) */
    .content{
        height: 100%;
        background-color: white;
    }
    /* Set gray background color and 100% height */
    .sidenav {
      padding-top: 20px;
      background-color: #3A6DBF;
      height: 100%;
    }
    .corps {
      background-color: white;
      height: 100%;
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .flash-notice{
    	background-color: green;
    	font-size: 1.5em;
    	text-align: center;
    }
    .col_label{
      width: 40%;
    }
    .col_champ{
      width: 60%;
    }
    .col_space{
        width: 100%;
        background-color: gray;
    }
    .col_space_resume{
        width: 100%;
    }
    #status{
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .navbar-brand {
        padding: 0px;
    }
    .navbar-brand>img {
        height: 100%;
        padding: 0px;
        width: 160px;
    }
    form ul{
        list-style-type: none;
        color: red;
        padding-left: 0;
    }
    .bouton_recom{
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    /* Set black background color, white text and some padding */
    footer {
      background-color: #132440;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      height: 100px
    }
    .mentions{
        padding-top: 30px;
    }
    lien_mentions:link,lien_mentions:visited,lien_mentions:hover,lien_mentions:active{
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
    }
    header {
    	background-image: url({{ asset('images/Louvre.jpg') }}); 
      height: 370px;
    }
    .image_presentation {
      padding-right: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      justify-content:center;
      float:left;
    }
    .cadre{
      background-color: #26497F;
      color: #FFC44D;
    }
    /* On small screens, set height to 'auto' for sidenav and grid */
    @media(max-width: 991px) {
        body{
            font-size: 2em;
        }
        .logo{
            width: 320px;
            height: 100px;
        }
        .container {
            padding-left: 15px;
            padding-right: 15px;
            width: inherit;
        }
        .navbar-header {
            float: none;
        }
        .navbar-inverse{
            float: none;
            padding: 0px;
        }
        .navbar-nav {
            float: none;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0px;
        }
        .navbar-nav>li {
            float: none;
        }
        .navbar-nav>li>a {
            padding-top: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

      .sidenav {
        height: auto;
        padding: 15px;
      }
        label {
            width: 80%;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: block;
        }
        input, #champs_input, .champs_input, .champs_country{
            width: 80%;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: block;
        }
      .row.content {height:auto;} 
      header{display: none;}
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="container navbar navbar-inverse">
    <div class="navbar-header">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href={{ path('cdp_booking_homepage')}}><img class ="logo" src ="{{ asset('images/logo-louvre.jpg') }}" alt="logo"></a>
    </div>
      <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
        <li class="active"><a href={{ path('cdp_booking_new')}}>Billetterie en ligne</a></li>
      </ul>
  </nav>
<header class="container bg-primary text-white">
  <div class="text-center">
    <h1>Musée du Louvre</h1>
    <p class="lead">Réservez vos billets pour visiter le musée du Louvre</p>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container text-center">
  <div class="row content">
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-9 text-left corps">
    	{% block body %}
    	{% endblock %}
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-3 sidenav">
      <div class="well cadre">
         <h2>Horaires</h2>
      	<p>Le musée est ouvert tous les jours
      		de 9h à 18h <br>
      		Fermé le mardi <br>
      		et les 1er mai, <br>
      		1er novembre et 25 décembre
     	</p>

      <hr>
      </div>
      <div class="well cadre">
        <h2>Tarifs</h2>
        <div class="text-left">
        	<h4>Journée :</h4>
     		<ul class="list-unstyled">
     			<li><b>Gratuit</b> pour les moins de 4 ans</li>
     			<li><b>8 €</b> de 4 ans à 12 ans</li> 
        		<li><b>16 €</b> à partir de 12 ans</li>   
        		<li><b>12 €</b> pour les plus de 60 ans</li>
        		<li><b>10 €</b> tarif réduit (étudiant, employé du musée, militaire…)</li>
      		</ul>
      		<h4>Demi-journée :</h4>
      		<ul class="list-unstyled">
      			<li><b>Gratuit</b> pour les moins de 4 ans</li>
     			<li><b>4 €</b> de 4 ans à 12 ans</li> 
        		<li><b>8 €</b> à partir de 12 ans</li>   
        		<li><b>6 €</b> pour les plus de 60 ans</li>
        		<li><b>5 €</b> tarif réduit (étudiant, employé du musée, militaire…)</li>
        	</ul>	
  		</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<footer class="container text-center">
    <div class ="mentions">
        <a class="lien_mentions" href="#">mentions légales</a>
    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>